    <h1>We Value Your Feedback</h1>
    <p>
      Your insights help us improve and tailor our platform to better meet your
      needs. Please share your thoughts on how we can enhance Student Assistant.
    </p>

    <h2>Share Your Feedback</h2>
    <p>
      We appreciate your time and effort in helping us make Student Assistant
      the best resource for learning to code. Your feedback is crucial for us to
      understand what works well and what can be improved.
    </p>
    <p>
      Please take a few minutes to fill out our feedback survey by clicking the
      link below:
    </p>
    <p><a href="URL_TO_SURVEY">Take the Feedback Survey</a></p>
    <p>
      This survey will ask you about various aspects of our platform, including:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Ease of use</li>
      <li>Content quality</li>
      <li>Personalization of learning paths</li>
      <li>Support and community interaction</li>
      <li>Overall satisfaction</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Why Your Feedback Matters</h2>
    <p>
      Your feedback directly influences the development and improvement of our
      services. It helps us:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Identify areas that need enhancement</li>
      <li>Understand user needs more comprehensively</li>
      <li>Create a more engaging and effective learning environment</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Thank You</h2>
    <p>
      Thank you for being a part of our community and for taking the time to
      help us grow and improve. We are committed to continuously refining our
      platform to serve you better.
    </p>
